latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Oobee is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Features
* Allow user-only install as non-admin on Windows in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/149

#### Improvements 
* Single user data directory per scan to support concurrent scans in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/521
* Replace blocked axios requests with Playwright (scan sitemap files, url check for pdf files, follow  robots.txt) in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/522
* Double mutation count to account for websites loading in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/524
* Move basic auth to Authorization header in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/525
* Process exit 1 when no pages can be scanned in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/526
* Resolve inconsistent user data directory created and deleted in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/527
* Multiple QOL improvements for engine reliability in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/528
* Uses new system info v2 to avoid wmic dependency in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/530
